properties.areaDesc: Waters from Point Pinos to Point Piedras Blancas 10-60 NM
properties.headline: Gale Warning issued January 4 at 2:38PM PST until January 5 at 9:00AM PST by NWS San Francisco CA
properties.description:
* WHAT...For the Gale Warning, north winds 20 to 30 kt with
gusts up to 35 kt and seas 11 to 13 feet at 13 seconds
expected. For the Small Craft Advisory, northwest winds 20 to
25 kt with gusts up to 30 kt and seas 10 to 11 feet at 13
seconds.

* WHERE...Waters from Point Pinos to Point Piedras Blancas 10-
60 NM.

* WHEN...For the Gale Warning, from 3 AM to 9 AM PST Sunday. For
the Small Craft Advisory, until 3 AM PST Sunday.

* IMPACTS...Strong winds will cause hazardous seas which could
capsize or damage vessels and reduce visibility.
properties.instruction:
Mariners should alter plans to avoid these hazardous conditions.
Remain in port, seek safe harbor, alter course, and/or secure the
vessel for severe conditions.

NWSheadline: SMALL CRAFT ADVISORY NOW IN EFFECT UNTIL 3 AM PST SUNDAY... ...GALE WARNING IN EFFECT FROM 3 AM TO 9 AM PST SUNDAY
